        "rich_text_8DL9Df": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>When subtlety meets sparkle, it creates an everlasting impression  and that’s exactly what Lucira Jewelry brings you with its diamond <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-nosepins\" title=\"nose pin\">nose pin</a> design collection. Designed for the modern woman who values tradition and elegance, our range combines timeless artistry with contemporary finesse. Whether you prefer a classic solitaire or a chic minimal stud, every piece in this collection is crafted to highlight your beauty and individuality.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bUfHBT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Beauty of a Diamond Nose Pin Design",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Beauty of a Diamond Nose Pin Design</h2>",
            "custom_id": "the-beauty"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_gEUkmH": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/What_is_a_22_Carat_Gold_Hallmark.jpg",
            "text": "<p>A diamond nose pin design is more than an accessory  it’s an expression of your heritage, confidence, and grace. At <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lucira Jewelry\">Lucira Jewelry</a>, we curate each nose pin using precision-cut lab-grown diamonds that shimmer with brilliance while being ethically sourced.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_JmwFBb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>From dainty daily wear styles to intricate festive pieces, our latest diamond nose pin design range offers something for everyone. Our artisans have mastered the art of balancing tradition with innovation, creating nose pins that blend effortlessly with both ethnic and western outfits. Explore our diamond nose pin design images to witness the sheer diversity of styles from delicate floral motifs to sleek geometric designs.</p><p>To experience these exquisite creations firsthand, visit the<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/chembur-store\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Chembur Lucira Store</span></a>, where our jewelry experts help you find a nose pin that truly complements your personality.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Jc4E4r": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Discover Modern Elegance – The Latest Diamond Nose Pin Designs",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Discover Modern Elegance – The Latest Diamond Nose Pin Designs</h2><p>If you’ve been searching for the latest diamond nose pin design, Lucira Jewelry has curated a breathtaking assortment that fits every mood and occasion. Each diamond nose pin design in our collection is meticulously crafted in gold, rose gold, and platinum finishes, ensuring durability and brilliance.</p><p>Our collection draws inspiration from Indian aesthetics, infused with a global sensibility. Whether it’s your first piercing or an upgrade to your existing collection, our designs promise to become your new favorite accessory.</p><p>For those who love pairing their jewelry, explore our<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/rose-gold-diamond-necklace\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">rose gold diamond necklace</span></a> collection a perfect complement to your diamond nose pin for festive and bridal occasions.</p>",
            "custom_id": "discover"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_6WCWXy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "A Glimpse into Lucira’s Signature Collections",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>A Glimpse into Lucira’s Signature Collections</h2>",
            "custom_id": "glimpse"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_AWtNat": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Components_of_a_22_Carat_Gold_Hallmark.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Lucira Jewelry believes that beauty should be effortless and everlasting. Our<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Collections</span></a> bring together pieces that resonate with modern sophistication. From earrings and pendants to statement necklaces, every creation tells a story of precision and purity.</p><p>If you adore sustainable brilliance, our<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-necklace\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">lab grown diamond necklace</span></a> range reflects ethical luxury at its finest. These pieces pair beautifully with any diamond nose pin design, offering a refined, coordinated look for every occasion.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xii4nX": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Diamond Nose Pin Designs with Price in India",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Diamond Nose Pin Designs with Price in India</h2>",
            "custom_id": "diamond"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_XJgEXF": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/How_to_Check_a_22_Carat_Gold_Hallmark_3e978921-1d2a-477d-b793-79806196b217.jpg",
            "text": "<p>At Lucira Jewelry, transparency is at the heart of our promise. Our diamond nose pin designs with price in India are displayed clearly, allowing you to shop confidently without hidden costs. Each diamond nose pin design represents the perfect balance of affordability, sustainability, and luxury.</p><p>If you’re curious about the overall value of lab-grown diamonds, our guide on<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/1-carat-lab-grown-diamond-price-in-india\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">1 carat lab grown diamond price in India</span></a> provides valuable insights into pricing and craftsmanship standards in the Indian market.</p><p>Lucira’s pricing ensures that every woman can own a diamond that reflects her style and individuality. Whether you’re shopping online or visiting our boutique, you’ll find a design that fits your preferences and budget.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_rQKzCe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Styling Your Diamond Nose Pin Design",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Styling Your Diamond Nose Pin Design</h2><p>A diamond nose pin design is versatile enough to enhance any outfit. For a minimalist look, choose a petite stud that pairs seamlessly with western attire. For traditional events or weddings, explore floral or swirl-patterned designs that radiate brilliance.</p><p>Our experts recommend pairing your nose pin with matching earrings from our<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-earrings\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">All Earrings Collection</span></a> for a complete look. Among our favorites are:</p><ol><li>Classic Diamond Stud Earrings – Understated elegance for daily wear.</li><li>Petite Halo Earrings – Surround your sparkle with a circle of brilliance.</li><li>Twist Hoop Earrings – A modern, bold statement that complements your diamond nose pin.</li></ol><p>Each style highlights the understated beauty of Lucira’s craftsmanship, creating an effortless harmony between all your jewelry pieces.</p>",
            "custom_id": "styling"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ADDTPa": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Craftsmanship Behind Every Design",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Craftsmanship Behind Every Design</h2><p>Every diamond nose pin design at Lucira Jewelry is a result of meticulous craftsmanship and advanced technology. Our artisans use precision tools to set each diamond securely, ensuring both comfort and longevity. The result is a collection that balances innovation, culture, and ethical luxury.</p><p>Our pieces celebrate individuality  designed for women who prefer quality over quantity. Lucira’s nose pins are durable, hypoallergenic, and crafted to retain their sparkle for years.</p>",
            "custom_id": "the"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_7bxGmb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Choose Lucira Jewelry?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Choose Lucira Jewelry?</h2><p>Lucira Jewelry stands apart for its fusion of contemporary elegance and sustainable craftsmanship. Each diamond nose pin design is created with care, using only certified lab-grown diamonds. These stones are physically and chemically identical to mined diamonds but have a smaller environmental footprint.</p><p>Whether you’re gifting a loved one or indulging yourself, Lucira ensures an experience marked by trust, quality, and beauty. Our online store offers a seamless shopping journey, supported by transparent policies and detailed product descriptions.</p>",
            "custom_id": "why"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_CNg3En": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Experience Timeless Beauty with Lucira",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Experience Timeless Beauty with Lucira</h2><p>Your diamond nose pin design is more than an ornament it’s a reflection of your individuality and sophistication. At <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lucira Jewelry</span></a>, we invite you to explore our world of ethical luxury, where every sparkle is a story of precision, purity, and purpose. Discover your perfect design today, and let your radiance shine with Lucira.</p>",
